snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls: Legends - Moons of Elsweyr Official Trailer
snippet.description:
As new conflicts emerge in the ancestral home of the Khajiit, so too does the next expansion for The Elder Scrolls: Legends with Moons of Elweyr!

Coming June 27th
MAKE YOUR PLAY - Pre-Order Now!

Follow The Elder Scrolls: Legends on social media: 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TESLegends 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/TESLegends 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TESLegends"

ESRB RATING: TEEN with Fantasy Violence and Mild Blood.
